caption: Celebrating Marie Claire’s Women of the Year Awards surrounded by the most inspiring female collective that are shaping our future and, quite literally, saving lives. From fighting injustice, broken systems, inequality, climate change and even finding a cure for melanoma cancer — these women give me so much hope for the future my daughter is going to grow up in. There were many tears last night. Thank you for having me @marieclaireau & @georgiecmccourt 🤍
